e distributed in different interstellar\nenvironments, making the evaluation of column density ratios between such\nisomers irrelevant unless it can be independently shown that these species are\nco-spatial.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2005 17:15:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
